snippet.textDisplay:
There isn't Five Rivers (Panj-Aab). Sindu / Indus, Comes from the Hindu Kush Mountains. Jehlum and Chenaab, Come from Kashmir. Ravi comes From Himachal. Himachal's, Other River is Ganga.
Beas, that's Your Trick to Come onto Your Field. Like "Prima Vera de la Monde". Saath-Ruj = Seven Fills of Water.
You Haven't got Five or Seven Rivers. There's only Four, Indus, Jehlum, Chenaab and Ravi. I've Seen Beas, it was Hardly Moving.
